{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cedc4e377a","title":"毛泽东在上海动力学校的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"03d50d4e08","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":1,"articleId":"cedc4e377a"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c232c847c6","type":"title","text":"毛泽东在上海动力学校的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"d12bfcb1e9","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"b0fdb9e13a","type":"paragraph","text":"要青年学生去打杂扫地，也不是一件坏事情啊！我看对青年一定得加强思想政治工作，要教育青年不要轻视劳动，要愿意参加集体劳动，才能建设好我们的国家！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"d672870dc6","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"81db7e74fc","type":"paragraph","text":"在贯彻执行中央命令的过程中，也必须走好群众路线，进行说服教育。青年学生除了学习专业以外，在思想上、政治上必须要有进步，要有正确的政治观点，否则很容易为右派分子所利用。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"71162e6d6b","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"eabec3de31","type":"paragraph","text":"青年，即使是青年工人，因为没有受过旧社会的苦，更应该加强阶级教育，提高他们的思想觉悟。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"451b853142","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"},{"id":"3d1d1d70cd","type":"paragraph","text":"对青年一定要加强阶级教育，提高他们的阶级觉悟，叫他们向优秀的工人学习。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a"}],"page":{"id":"edda2e5035","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedc4e377a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}